commits.message:
Remove Evidently feature flags from Terraform (#1058)

The Evidently product was EOL'd by AWS effective Oct 17, 2025.
Therefore, any deploys after that date will fail since Terraform is
unable to access those resources.

See this commit from our upstream infra codebase:
https://github.com/navapbc/template-infra/commit/94b4dd013867710b799da1bbed565b64688c7cdc
commits.author: Tom Dooner

Add chromedriver upgrade to `bin/update` (#1052)

This script is meant to upgrade all dependencies. Since chromedriver is
particularly nagging, let's see if we can make it automatically upgrade
using homebrew.

Not sure if the `xattr` thing will work to get around the security
thing, but would be awesome if it did. (I tried it once successfully.)
